problem_text: Robert Lewandowski is a striker. [BG] Strikers are soccer players. Robert Lewandowski left Bayern Munchen. [BG] If a player left a team they no longer play for that team.
predicates:
Striker(x) ::: x is a striker.
SoccerPlayer(x) ::: x is a soccer player.
Left(x, y) ::: x left team y.
PlaysFor(x, y) ::: x plays for team y.

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski no longer plays for Bayern Munchen.
tests.conclusions: ¬PlaysFor(robert Lewandowski, bayern munchen) ::: Robert Lewandowski no longer plays for Bayern Munchen. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a soccer player and he left Bayern Munchen.
tests.conclusions: SoccerPlayer(robert) ∧ Left(robert, bayernmunchen) ::: Robert Lewandowski is a soccer player and he left Bayern Munchen. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a soccer player and he left Bayern Munchen, and he no longer plays for Bayern Munchen.
tests.conclusions: SoccerPlayer(robert_lewandowski) ∧ Left(robert_lewandowski, bayern_munchen) ∧ ¬PlaysFor(robert_lewandowski, bayern_munchen) ::: Robert Lewandowski is a soccer player and he left Bayern Munchen, and he no longer plays for Bayern Munchen. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a soccer player who left Bayern Munchen and no longer plays for Bayern Munchen.
Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a striker and plays for Bayern Munchen.
tests.conclusions: Striker(robert_lewandowski) ∧ PlaysFor(robert_lewandowski, bayern_munchen) ::: Robert Lewandowski is a striker and plays for Bayern Munchen. FALSE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a soccer player and he no longer plays for Bayern Munchen.
Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a soccer player who plays for Bayern Munchen and left Bayern Munchen.
tests.conclusions: SoccerPlayer(robert_lewandowski) ∧ PlaysFor(robert_lewandowski, bayern_munchen) ∧ Left(robert_lewandowski, bayern_munchen) ::: FALSE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a striker and he plays for Bayern Munchen.
Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a striker, and if he left Bayern Munchen, then he does not play for Bayern Munchen.
Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Robert Lewandowski is a striker, and he no longer plays for Bayern Munchen.
